## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **API Keys Needed:** You'll need to get a **Groq API key** (free at console.groq.com) for the AI Council to work. I'll also optionally support FRED API key for live economic data. I'll document everything you need in a `TODO.md`.

> [!WARNING]
> **Scope Decision:** The blueprint has ~30 features. For a working, polished product by June 1, I'm prioritizing:
> 1. ✅ Stunning onboarding wizard (Financial Twin Genesis)
> 2. ✅ Full AI Council deliberation system (3 agents with debate)
> 3. ✅ 3 pre-built scenarios with AI variation
> 4. ✅ 3D Galaxy visualization with WebGPU
> 5. ✅ Time scrubber + parallel timeline preview
> 6. ✅ Financial Mastery scoring + decision history dashboard
> 7. ❌ Plaid bank linking (post-hackathon)
> 8. ❌ Multiplayer/classroom mode (post-hackathon)
> 9. ❌ Real-time live market data streaming (post-hackathon — using curated historical data instead)
> 
> Does this prioritization work for you?

