## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Backend: `pytest` for simulation math (compound interest, tax brackets, consequence calculations)
- Frontend: Manual browser testing via the browser tool

### Manual Verification
1. Complete full onboarding flow → verify twin generation
2. Play through all 3 scenarios → verify AI council deliberation works
3. Verify 3D galaxy renders and responds to simulation state
4. Test time scrubber, parallel timelines, risk storm effects
5. Check responsive design on mobile viewport
6. Verify "See the Future" preview renders correctly
7. Test with and without API keys (graceful degradation)

### Browser Testing
- Run dev server and test full user flow end-to-end
- Screenshot key states for walkthrough
